{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"jq9pfv8ovu2k5ey4vhgvghw","title":"新语","desc":"","updated":1651801743636,"created":1651801327263,"custom":{},"fname":"censorship.newspeak","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"f68051496c6569054bf9c75f7d1f4d21","links":[],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"qAItL5nac0TIpD7Uv7eB5","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"新语\">新语<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#新语\"></a></h1>\n<p>新语(Newspeak)是乔治·奥威尔的作品《1984》中对审查者使用的一种洗脑手段的描述<a id=\"fnref-1\" class=\"fnref\" href=\"#fn-1\">1</a>。</p>\n<p>在中国的武汉肺炎疫情中，官方为了加强舆论控制，在宣传和沟通中使用了大量新语：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>嚴防死守、清零、動態清零、社會面清零、封閉式管理、按下暫停鍵、按下慢行鍵、全域靜態管理、臨時社會面管控、相對靜止、全城靜默管理、原地不動、靜下來了</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"footnotes\">Footnotes<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#footnotes\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><span id=\"fn-1\" style=\"width: 0; height: 0;\"></span><p><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E8%AA%9E_(%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%9D%E5%85%AB%E5%9B%9B)\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E8%AA%9E_(%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%9D%E5%85%AB%E5%9B%9B)</a><a class=\"fn\" href=\"#fnref-1\">˄</a></p></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","title":"墙国地图","desc":"","updated":1646712715590,"created":1644382378522,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"02c3c0c9e63ff90b668e6396d3f28d2a","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"underlying","alias":"实现方法","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":3,"offset":213},"end":{"line":12,"column":22,"offset":232},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"underlying"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"underlying","alias":"开源工具","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":3,"offset":382},"end":{"line":15,"column":24,"offset":403},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fna